_sText:
After unsuccessfully attacking the factory, the terrorists are now targetting the factory's access bridge.

Terrorists: Destroy the bridge or attempt to flood it by destroying the power plant upstream.

Counter-terrorists: Prevent the terrorists from restricting access to the factory.

Map By: PureKnickers (www.knixgeekout.blogspot.com)
Special Thanks to Sunny, all the testers and the Shire.
